These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing, puzzles, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, water-polo, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | chess    | puzzles      | photography |
| Sport   | cycling   | water-polo | ice-hockey | baseball        |

