.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, american, japanese, indonesian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, amaryllis, dahlia
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the person who growsaconite##1
6. the person driving the roller is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Nationality        | japanese   | american | polish     | indonesian      |
| Flower         | sunflower | amaryllis | dahlia | aconite |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, dannemann, old-henry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, drama, horror, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is the person watching horror movies##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Cigar         | bolivar | alhambra | dannemann | old-henry |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | drama    | sports | horror     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

