.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, orchid, sunflower
4 different pets are kept: rat, horse, chinchilla, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rat is the person who growsorchid##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Flower         | lily | sunflower | orchid | aconite |
| Pet       | horse     | lizard      | rat     | chinchilla      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

