.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
City: san-francisco, paris, edinburgh, marseilles
House: cape-cod, victorian, cottage, art-deco
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the cape-cod house is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the victorian house##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person traveling to paris##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| City   | edinburgh  | san-francisco        | marseilles  | paris       |
| House         | cape-cod | cottage    | victorian | art-deco |

