.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, aristoff, siglo, bongani
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, board-games, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the chaman-smoker is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the siglo-smoker##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
8. the bongani-smoker is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar           | aristoff | siglo | bongani | chaman |
| Hobby   | traveling   | board-games  | rock-climbing | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

