.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, december, june
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, chinese, polish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the chinese is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the italian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the nigerian is on the right of the italian##1
8. the italian is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday          | july  | june | december   | may     |
| Nationality         | polish | italian   | nigerian  | chinese |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

