.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, indie, dubstep, hip-hop
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dunhill, baccarat, prince
1. the fan of indie is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the prince-smoker is the fan of dubstep##1
7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
8. the fan of indie is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop | dubstep     | salsa | indie |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Cigar   | dunhill   | prince | montecristo    | baccarat |

