.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, jazz, punk
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, rat, rabbit
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the owner of the rat is the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage          | juice        | soy-milk   | cola  | fanta   |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | punk     | d&b    | jazz       |
| Pet         | ferret | dog | rat | rabbit |

