The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, orchid, marigold
City: colone, san-francisco, berlin, marseilles
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | iced-tea | mirinda | 7up        |
| Flower       | marigold | azalea  | daffodil | orchid     |
| City        | san-francisco    | berlin   | marseilles  | colone |

