.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, dutch, indian, australian
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, singing, cooking, chess
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the australian##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Nationality         | german  | australian | dutch  | indian |
| Hobby       | cooking | singing        | chess | photography       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

