.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, guinea-pig, horse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, d&b, dubstep, disco
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the lizard is the fan of dubstep##1
7. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | horse   | guinea-pig   | lizard | rabbit |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | house  | dubstep  | d&b  |

