.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, malaysian, thai
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, rock, trance
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, yellow, apricot, brown
1. the russian is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the fan of trance##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Nationality         | thai | russian    | indian        | malaysian |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Color         | yellow   | chestnut | apricot | brown  |

