.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, august, november
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, kiwi, onion, orange
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, motorbike, roller
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating orange##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person eating onion##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | april   | november  | may    | august    |
| Food   | orange | onion  | strawberry  | kiwi |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

