.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, may, october, november
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, monopoly, scrabble
1. the person playing bridge is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking water##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in august##1
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Birthday   | august        | november   | may  | october  |
| Game         | scrabble | mah-jongg | monopoly   | bridge |

