.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball, skateboarding, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, snowmobile, motorbike
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, horse, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Sport          | biathlon     | lacrosse   | skateboarding | basketball |
| Transport   | car | motorbike | snowmobile | taxi   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

