.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, scientist, security-guard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, amaryllis, poppy
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly
1. the engineer is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsiris is the person playing bridge##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Flower   | poppy   | iris | aconite   | amaryllis      |
| Game         | domino | bridge    | mah-jongg   | monopoly         |

 